BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:287@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260430
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260501
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym -  Taster Session
DESCRIPTION:An introductory 45-minute taster session for the Parent Gym programme.\n\nParent Gym is coming to Belleville Wix Academy. This 45-minute taster session introduces a six-week programme that shares practical tips and strategies to make family life easier and help children thrive. All parents are welcome to apply, and places will be filled on a first-come, first-served basis. The programme is free for parents. Please contact the school or Ellie Wilkes (KS1 lead) to confirm your place.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:288@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260507
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260508
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym Week 1 -  Chat
DESCRIPTION:The first session of the Parent Gym programme focusing on communication ('Chat').\n\nParent Gym is a well-established, six-week programme exploring practical tips and strategies for parenting. This first weekly session, titled 'Chat', lasts two hours. The programme is free and open to all parents, but registration is required on a first-come, first-served basis.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:289@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260521
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260522
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym Week 2 -  Love
DESCRIPTION:The second session of Parent Gym focusing on building relationships ('Love').\n\nThe second weekly two-hour session of the Parent Gym programme. Note there is no session on 14th May. This session focuses on 'Love'. Registration via the school or Ellie Wilkes is required.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:290@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260604
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260605
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym Week 3 -  Behave
DESCRIPTION:The third session of Parent Gym focusing on boundaries and behavior ('Behave').\n\nFollowing the half-term break (no session on 28th May), the Parent Gym programme resumes with Week 3: 'Behave'. A two-hour session from 9am to 11am for registered participants.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:291@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260611
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260612
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym Week 4 -  Care
DESCRIPTION:The fourth session of Parent Gym focusing on health and wellbeing ('Care').\n\nThe fourth weekly two-hour session of the Parent Gym programme focusing on 'Care'. Held in school from 9am to 11am.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:292@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260618
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260619
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym Week 5 -  Discover
DESCRIPTION:The fifth session of Parent Gym focusing on learning and play ('Discover').\n\nThe fifth weekly two-hour session of the Parent Gym programme focusing on 'Discover'. Held in school from 9am to 11am.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:293@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260626
SUMMARY:BWA: Parent Gym Week 6 -  Together
DESCRIPTION:The final session of Parent Gym focusing on family harmony ('Together').\n\nThe concluding weekly two-hour session of the Parent Gym programme. This session is titled 'Together'. Held in school from 9am to 11am.
CATEGORIES:WELLBEING
END:VEVENT
