BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:334@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260515
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260516
SUMMARY:BWA: International Families Day
DESCRIPTION:School-wide celebration of diverse heritage including a homework project, national dress day, and an after-school international buffet.\n\nInternational Families Day at BWA. Pupils are invited to complete a heritage homework project (due 11th May). On 15th May, pupils may wear national dress or flag colours. Parents are invited to volunteer to share culture/skills (form due 8th May). An international buffet will be held in the lower hall from 3:30pm; food donations requested (bring to office from 2:30pm). All food must be nut-free.
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
